metadata.name: MECHA #45

attributes.value: Custom Trained Ai Advanced SD + Color grading

metadata.description:
The art collection showcases a vibrant fusion of feminine grace and mechanical might. 
Meanwhile, the incorporation of Robotech influences adds a futuristic edge to the overall aesthetic, creating a dynamic contrast between the delicate and the powerful. This collection invites the viewer to experience a fusion of emotions, from awe-inspiring excitement to tender nostalgia, and leaves a lasting impression.
.
Driven pencil Doodles + Ai + Color grading
.
By Hackerman HKDAO Collective
